      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary specimen, preserved in showroom condition. This vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class, featuring a flawless exterior and an interior that retains its original luster. Meticulously maintained and mechanically beyond reproach, it offers a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a truly pristine asset. This is a turnkey acquisition for those who demand uncompromising standards.",
