    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute showroom-quality 2021 Audi RS5 Sportback in Nardo Gray. This vehicle has been meticulously pampered since day one, stored in a climate-controlled garage and hand-washed weekly. The exterior paint retains its factory depth and luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating with zero stone chips or swirl marks. Inside, the Fine Nappa leather remains supple and pristine, still carrying that distinct new-car aroma; there are no creases on the bolsters and the carbon fiber inlays are flawless. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, with every service performed ahead of schedule at an authorized dealership\u2014full documentation included. With ultra-low mileage and not a single blemish to be found, this is as close to a new vehicle as you can get on the secondary market. Experience uncompromising performance and prestige in a car that truly looks and drives like it just rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
